communications.subject: Freedom of Information Act Request: Nellis Air Force Base
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Any reports or documents pertaining to the cancelation of the annual Drag Brunch at Nellis Air Force base, located Northeast of Las Vegas Nevada from January 2021 to June 2023.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Alexandra

communications.subject: California Public Records Act Request: Booking number and arrest records
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the California Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

Any arrest records, video footage and criminal charges for an inmate awaiting trial named Nicolas Andrew Flores from January 2018 to October 2023.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Alexandra

communications.subject: Freedom of Information Act Request: Real Property in Reno Nevada
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Materials from the period from August 1, 2022 through August 31, 2023 describing the purchase of “real property,” including land and buildings, by or for use by Immigrations and Customs Enforcement in Reno, Nevada. “Federal real property” is defined as “any real property owned, leased, or otherwise managed by the Federal Government, both within and outside the United States, and improvements on Federal lands.”

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Alexandra
